Izzy Brown has spoken of the incredible weekend that saw him inspire Chelsea 's youth team to glory in the UEFA Youth League .
The Blues ' under 19 captain played the full 90 minutes of Roma 's 4-0 semi-final win over Roma on Friday afternoon after learning that Mourinho wanted him on the bench for the Premier League clash at Queens Park Rangers on Sunday .
18-year-old scored twice in the 3-2 final win over Shakhtar Donetsk to lift the Youth League trophy .